ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectProvincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 266, Quebec
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER No. 266 in order to (1) declare the natural disaster to be of concern to the federal government; and (2) authorize the provision of financial assistance to Québec with respect to spring flood that occurred in Québec from April 7 to may 11, 2023.
